{"title":"村头河埠上","authors":["崔汝先"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":10,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头河埠上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崔汝先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红霞天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫霞天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头河埠上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣声鼓声绕云天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出什么喜事了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑压压的人群一大片？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳荫下映出大横幅："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎工人大哥来支援！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红领巾忙着唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老年人睁圆了眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社长站在石阶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现出了满脸笑容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀，来了，来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五条彩船一线牵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披红挂绿好热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水也乐得忙把笑波添。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突击出来的打稻机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新刷的油漆还未干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚造好的化肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压得船船水满舷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一群小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个热火藏心坎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一袋工具一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心到公社把技术来相传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂长立船头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限热情填心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援农业机械化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农联盟万万年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没等船靠近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声好像浪拍岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老奶奶端来香茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女们托出土产当茶点……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂长社长肩并肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句话儿心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撕下红霞当纸张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也难把工农情谊来写尽！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}